// {type:class}
// {direction:topDown}
[JSON Schema Payload (from Server)]-fetch>[Network & Cache Layer]
[Network & Cache Layer]-payload>[Parser & Mapper]

[Parser & Mapper]-init variables>[State Management (Zustand/Redux)]
[Parser & Mapper]-extract layout>[Execution Engine (Recursive Renderer)]
[Parser & Mapper]-extract rules>[Rule Engine (Evaluator)]

[State Management (Zustand/Redux)]-subscribe/bind>[Execution Engine (Recursive Renderer)]
[Rule Engine (Evaluator)]-compute dynamic styles/visibility>[State Management (Zustand/Redux)]

[Execution Engine (Recursive Renderer)]-lookup component>[Component Registry]
[Component Registry]^[Core UI Components (Button, Text, Input)]
[Component Registry]^[Custom Widgets (Chart, Video Player)]

[Execution Engine (Recursive Renderer)]-render>[React Virtual DOM]
[React Virtual DOM]-user interactions (click, type)>[Action Resolver]

[Action Resolver]-mutate state>[State Management (Zustand/Redux)]
[Action Resolver]-trigger evaluation>[Rule Engine (Evaluator)]
[Action Resolver]-fire network request>[Network & Cache Layer]
